Kallie Flynn Childress https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Kallie_Flynn_Childress 0 Kallie Flynn Childress (born April 13, 1988) is an American actress. She is best known for her role as Yancy in the 2004 film Sleepover, for which won a Young Artist Award for Best Performance in a Feature Film - Supporting Young Actress at the 2005 ceremony.
